						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year: ⎯⎯</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to record some repairs to the shrine of the goddess Aṟamvaḷarttaammaṉ in the temple of Kulasēkharanātha at Kāriśēri by a native of Āḷvārtirunagari. This inscription is in characters of the 15th century A.D.</p>						

